dct_title_s: Laurel Springs, Camden County, New Jersey : including Laurel Springs Manor & Stratford (Sheet 1)
dct_description_sm: "December 1922." Includes location map, key, streets and specials index and text. "5597." Historic Maps copy has sheets 1-6, 9 and 11, showing Laurel Springs, and sheet 10, showing Stratford; sheets 7-8, showing Laurel Springs Manor, foldered separately.
